com.google.appinventor.client.explorer.project

Interface ProjectChangeListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AssetList, AssetManager, ProjectChangeAdapter, YaProjectEditor, YoungAndroidAssetSelectorPropertyEditor

    public interface ProjectChangeListener
    Listener interface for project change events.

    Classes interested in processing project changes must implement this interface, and instances of that class are registered with the Project instances using their Project.addProjectChangeListener(ProjectChangeListener) method. When a project node is added, the listeners' onProjectNodeAdded(Project, ProjectNode) methods will be invoked. When a project node is removed, the listeners' onProjectNodeRemoved(Project, ProjectNode) methods will be invoked.
